
---------------------
Introduction
---------------------
mcts-tablet-tests is an collection of mcts test cases for tablet testing. It depens on mcts components.

Before running mcts-tablet-tests, you need first install required mcts components.


---------------------
Build and Run
---------------------
+ Build in meego system, you need install build system and rpmbuild
cd mcts-tablet-tests
./pack.sh

This will generate mcts-tablet-tests-0.1-1.i386.rpm

+ Install
rpm -ivh mcts-tablet-tests-0.1-1.i386.rpm --nodeps

+ Test environment setup
Refer the section Test environment setup for all related mcts components

+ Run
testrunner-lite -a -f /usr/share/mcts-tablet-tests/tests.xml -o results.xml
Please refer to the section Test Envrionment setup for what to test


---------------------
Common Install
---------------------
./autogen
./configure prefix=/usr
make && make install


